title: Maxed Strength Necromancer
alternative_titles: Li Liang Dian Man? Wo Keshi Wangling Fashi A!
Maxed Strength Stat Points? But I'm a Necromancer!
力量点满？我可是亡灵法师啊！
summary: Maxed Strength Necromancer Manhua Qiao Yu enters the world of the meta-Universe and gains the hidden class of a Necromancer. Unfortunately, his initial intelligence and spirit stats are both at 0, and he even draws a strangely unique talent. In a fit of anger, Qiao Yu puts all his attribute points into strength! Who says a Necromancer can’t engage in hand-to-hand combat? As Qiao Yu punches the World serpent, Yemojia, to death, players in the meta-Universe are driven mad. Bro, please, stop brawling! You’re a Necromancer! Just summon an undead, please! Li Liang Dian Man? Wo Keshi Wangling Fashi A! Maxed Strength Stat Points? But I’m a Necromancer!
